description:
This is a 24 minute workout called 'Follow Along 20 Minute Beginner Calisthenics Home Workout' from the channel Summerfunfitness.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Hey Fam! This follow along calisthenics workout is aimed at helping all those people looking to improve their core and general body strength. Grab your mat, workout gear (or PJ's, im not judging) and follow along with this calisthenics beginner workout to get you started on your calisthenics journey.

Remember, do the reps that work for you. You don't have to go as fast as me or do as many reps as me. The more you practice, the stronger and therefore the better you will get!

Intro: 0:00
Beginner Calisthenics Workout: 1:21
